## Soviet Union

The [Soviet Union](/Soviet_Union), officially the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics (USSR), was a [socialist state](/socialist_state) that spanned much of [Eurasia](/Eurasia) from 1922 to 1991. It was a peculiar beast, a sprawling entity built on ideals that, in practice, often led to… complications. Think of it as a grand experiment, one that ended with a rather spectacular implosion.

